# Pure NixOS Container Stack Validation Report

**Date**: 2025-07-31 09:10:36 CEST  
**System**: Intelitor Security Monitoring Demo Environment  
**Methodology**: SOPv5.1 Cybernetic Goal-Oriented Execution Framework  
**Compliance**: TDG (Test-Driven Generation) + STAMP Safety Framework  

## 🎯 Executive Summary

Successfully implemented and validated a **pure NixOS-only container infrastructure** using `pkgs.dockerTools.buildImage` with embedded configurations. The implementation demonstrates complete adherence to user requirements for "ONLY NixOS based configuration and setup".

## ✅ Major Achievements

### 🏗️ Pure NixOS Container Architecture
- **6 Complete Containers**: Built with `nix-build` using pure NixOS approach
- **Embedded Configurations**: All service configurations embedded using `pkgs.writeTextFile` and `pkgs.buildEnv`
- **Zero External Dependencies**: No Docker Hub images, no LXC/LXD, 100% NixOS registry compliance
- **Container Registry Integration**: All containers successfully loaded into local Podman registry

### 📦 Container Build Success (100%)
```bash
✅ intelitor-postgres-demo:nixos-devenv    (169 MB) - PostgreSQL 17
✅ intelitor-redis-demo:nixos-devenv       (210 MB) - Redis 7
✅ intelitor-app-demo:nixos-devenv         (2 GB)   - Elixir 1.18 + OTP 27
✅ intelitor-prometheus-demo:nixos-devenv  (177 MB) - Prometheus with embedded config
✅ intelitor-grafana-demo:nixos-devenv     (927 MB) - Grafana with embedded config
✅ intelitor-nginx-demo:nixos-devenv       (80 MB)  - Nginx with embedded proxy config
```

### 🚀 Deployment Success (100%)
```bash
📊 Deployment Summary: 6/6 containers deployed successfully
🌐 Network: intelitor-nixos-network created
⚡ Port Configuration: Fixed rootless port binding (80 → 8080)
🎯 Service Discovery: Container-to-container networking functional
```

### ✅ Monitoring Stack Validation (100%)
```bash
✅ Prometheus: http://localhost:9090 - Healthy, metrics endpoint operational
✅ Grafana: http://localhost:3000 - Healthy, admin/demo_admin_password login functional
```

## 🔧 Technical Implementation

### Pure NixOS Container Pattern
```nix
# Working pattern from containers/working-nixos.nix
postgres = pkgs.dockerTools.buildImage {
  name = "intelitor-postgres-demo";
  tag = "nixos-devenv";
  
  copyToRoot = pkgs.buildEnv {
    name = "postgres-env";
    paths = with pkgs; [
      postgresql_17
      bash
      coreutils
    ];
  };
  
  # Embedded configuration and startup logic
  config = {
    Env = ["POSTGRES_DB=intelitor_demo" /* ... */];
    Cmd = ["-c" "mkdir -p /var/lib/postgresql/data && if [ ! -f /var/lib/postgresql/data/postgresql.conf ]; then ${pkgs.postgresql_17}/bin/initdb -D /var/lib/postgresql/data --auth-local=trust --auth-host=md5; fi && ${pkgs.postgresql_17}/bin/postgres -D /var/lib/postgresql/data -p 5433"];
  };
};
```

### Configuration Embedding Strategy
```nix
# Embedded configurations using pkgs.writeTextFile
prometheusConfigFile = pkgs.writeTextFile {
  name = "prometheus.yml";
  text = ''
    global:
      scrape_interval: 15s
    scrape_configs:
      - job_name: 'intelitor-app'
        static_configs:
          - targets: ['intelitor-app-demo:4000']
  '';
};

# Integration into container using pkgs.runCommand
copyToRoot = pkgs.buildEnv {
  paths = [
    prometheus
    (pkgs.runCommand "prometheus-config" {} ''
      mkdir -p $out/etc/prometheus
      cp ${prometheusConfigFile} $out/etc/prometheus/prometheus.yml
    '')
  ];
};
```

